1. make
	Compiles TalkSoup
	
2. make install
	Installs TalkSoup *must be done as root*
	
	You can also install TalkSoup as a regular user by doing a 
	GNUSTEP_INSTALLATION_DIR="$GNUSTEP_USER_ROOT" make install
	which will install it into $HOME/GNUstep
	
3. gopen TalkSoup.app
	Run TalkSoup

Enjoy!

